title: Skue Sparebank
text:
Skue Sparebank is a Norwegian <a href="savings%20bank">savings bank</a>, headquartered in <a href="Nesbyen">Nesbyen</a>, <a href="Norway">Norway</a>. The banks main market is
<a href="Buskerud">Buskerud</a>. The banks history goes back to 1842 with the establishment of Nes Prestegjelds Sparebank.
